              },
              "docs": "Temperature state. Usually reads `Normal`. All options from [Text Sensor](https://esphome.io/components/text_sensor/index.html#config-text-sensor).\n\n*See also: [pylontech Text Sensor](https://esphome.io/components/pylontech.html#id2)*"
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}